{"tid":218911,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雲加首度承認擬斟「新亨利」","createTime":"2017-04-26T23:20:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-26T23:42:29.000Z","uid":46892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"58f873cbd364015083d1eff85e57930b9e383b0c","tid":218911,"uid":46892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T23:20:57.000Z","msg":"[<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=RlZLtXxvTyjhSejQ4AJs48mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=c7da1e95\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】阿仙奴領隊雲加終於首度開腔承認，有意在今夏從摩納哥引入炙手可熱的「新亨利」基利安洛天，但又坦言未必可負擔這筆轉會費。<br />\n<br />\n早於今年初，雲加已向傳媒透露，自己密切觀察摩納哥新星基利安洛天（Kylian Mbappe Lottin）的發展，並覺得對方可能是新亨利，但證實有意羅致，到這天才是首次。他在周三聯賽打敗李斯特城前接受SFR Sport訪問說：「很明顯，如果說我們沒有注視他是虛偽及說謊。」<br />\n<br />\n「不過，他已獲大量球會，也許比我們更具財力的球會垂青。」近期與「新亨利」名字扯上關係的球會多不勝數，當中傳得最盛是西甲勁旅皇家馬德里。<br />\n<br />\n現年18歲的基利安洛天本季表現技驚四座，其中為摩納哥在歐聯先後擊敗曼城和多蒙特，從而取得4強一席，而他本人亦在上月取得法國國家隊第1頂cap帽。"},{"pid":"a8e08e6844252b2c6c5723c05320367e2c204fc0","tid":218911,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T23:25:36.000Z","msg":"幼齒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ec038991665e9df5445efbe28906a0ace4b5d6f","tid":218911,"uid":64131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T23:26:26.000Z","msg":"不如睇下亨利 安歷卡 柏金 維托特 簡奴 蘇加 亞倫史密夫啲親生仔 16歲未好過啦  起碼有佢地DNA"},{"pid":"ec5ffd919c12c179a253a748a0873215cd132081","tid":218911,"uid":3244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T23:26:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ce2a8935cc89de8d4b46d8299555231864f9de02","tid":218911,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T23:27:49.000Z","msg":"抬價部話億1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3a26584fa8b0d088e9bdbe5bc257def03218bdd","tid":218911,"uid":66839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T23:39:15.000Z","msg":"迷雲"},{"pid":"44369c034f3570efa527e1cd15ae42d4c5f91589","tid":218911,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T23:42:29.000Z","msg":"新享利原來又轉左人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}